-- Germany’s DIHK Praises Reforms in Crisis Nations, FTD Reports
-- B y   A n n e t t e   W e i s b a c h
-- 2012-08-28T17:53:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/germany-s-dihk-praises-reforms-in-crisis-nations-ftd-reports.html
Germany ’s DIHK chambers of industry
and trade praises reform progress in the peripheral euro-area
countries, Financial Times Deutschland reports, citing a study
commissioned by the newspaper with the trade group.  Unit labor costs in Ireland, Greece and Spain declined and
trade balance deficits are shrinking almost everywhere, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
